Third-party assets

The MIT license above covers the original source code, shaders, scene data, and
artwork authored for this project. Bundled third-party assets are NOT covered by
the MIT license and retain their own licenses. Each asset's author, license, and
source URL are recorded in full in CREDITS.md and are also shown inside the app
("設定 → この作品について").

Notably, this project bundles audio recordings and an image released under
Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike (CC BY-SA 3.0 / 4.0) and Creative
Commons Attribution (CC BY) licenses. Those works, and any direct adaptations of
them, remain under their respective CC licenses, with attribution provided in
CREDITS.md and in the in-app credits screen. Public-domain / CC0 assets carry no
restrictions. See CREDITS.md for the authoritative, per-asset record.
